{"tid":1470383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[向大陸電Say No] 長遠減碳策略公眾諮詢","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:58:19.000Z","uid":267806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ef3d9db56d45f2397dd7e38fcb53f2aedc37f7","tid":1470383,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"因為開過係政事台冇乜人理所以我係時事台到開多次<br />\n<br />\n可能依家風頭火勢大家冇左件事<br />\n但係我要提提大家記得去報名參加公眾諮詢會啊！！！<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\">今日同聽日</span>就舉行架啦！！<br />\n快d報名啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/register.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fregister.php&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=16de7d12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/tc/register.php</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有千其唔好唔記得公眾諮詢期deadline係9月20號<br />\n即係9月20號之前要表明反對向大陸買電啊！<br />\n填form唔夠架，最好要send埋一份有理有據的意見書，仲要要求回覆先有最大效果。<br />\n個向大陸買電計劃你可以禁上面條link耐心d睇<br />\n個仆街政府係搵埋歐盟國家有renewable energy既互相聯網為理據，要香港效發佢地向大陸買更多核電！<br />\n注意，係更多，唔好同我講大亞灣已經係乜乜77<br />\n目前小妹大約諗左幾個point，希望可以拋鏄引玉，可以諗到更多更好同完善好呢d論點<br />\n<br />\n1. 核電比碳排放影響更深遠，以環保角度而言，不應單單為減碳而增加本就受爭議的核電比例，否則只係為跑數而跑數，而非真正為環保<br />\n<br />\n2. 現在中電同港燈都計劃增加天然氣比例，不但正在興建新的燃氣發電機組，堆填區焚化爐（定燒堆填區廢氣唔記得左，仲有計劃興建嘅液化天然氣接收站，太陽能Feed-in Tariff鼓勵發展太陽能等等，買大陸電完全係多此一舉<br />\n<br />\n3. 眾所周知香港的供電穩定性係全球首屈一指，兩間香港電力公司的穩定度至少皆有99.999℅（希望冇錯），而中國南方電網的穩定度遠遠低於香港（實際數字唔記得）。 難道為左環保，我地就要犧牲更多停電的風險嗎？香港停一次電的經濟損失可以數以千萬計，你擔當得起嗎？<br />\n<br />\n4. Paris Agreement畢竟冇legal binding force，點解要將個deadline set到咁快呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家記得唔好跟政府提供嘅思路誤導，要問出香港市民關心嘅，就要自己dup意見書<br />\n<br />\n而最最最緊急嘅係，記得報名參加公眾討論會啊！！！<br />\n強烈建議禁返我上面po條link睇哂個proposal寫左咩，然後對症下藥準備論據質詢。<br />\n<br />\n和理非們，做野啦！！！"},{"pid":"2a647a19313eb34449223854305b7985483e6afe","tid":1470383,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人係有去過公眾討論會可以分享下傾過d咩"},{"pid":"8c87e5eab6a61b2c5109754224d3d71bda603fc2","tid":1470383,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a3df2b42134b071af127d4dd2115551ebd65f9","tid":1470383,"uid":108360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"17565e995c9ab1a092cdb58a581ceba697f3375d","tid":1470383,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh a"},{"pid":"ce7a419eacf21938eada84282779e27aecee0d1b","tid":1470383,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e0b48464bf1f41214ec7bb0fa27f85e94c0ed10","tid":1470383,"uid":120722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319abbac8b4c008b9c4f904469cb217b88e06e2f","tid":1470383,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d397b9b3ae66c879ba6139bab3373ecdf2a4a8","tid":1470383,"uid":267806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkg